:[]},{"id":33106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/first-thing-prophet-does\/","url_meta":{"origin":25637,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: First thing the Prophet does at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Shurayh reported: I asked Aisha, saying, \u201cWhat was the first thing the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did when he entered his house?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cUse the toothstick.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 253 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062d\u064d \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0623\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/prophet-siwak-wake-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":25637,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Miswak: The Prophet cleans his teeth after waking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, arose at night, he would clean his mouth with the toothstick. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 243, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 255 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\